Lamento informarles...
... de que rechazo su carta de rechazo. Eso es lo que dicen en <a href="http://www.jkador.com/letter.htm">Dear ......,</a>.

<blockquote>
Despite your companys outstanding qualifications and previous experience in rejecting applicants, I find that your rejection does not meet with my requirements at this time. As a result, I will be starting employment with your firm on the first of the month. 
</blockquote>

Gente animosa. Leido en <a href="http://www.brunningonline.net/simon/blog/archives/001387.html">Rejection Rejection</a>.

